 Time Schedule   Dean s Evening Lecture Period Schedule   Evening Lecture Hours is time reserved for academic activities in the evening  This may include lectures  study groups  and extra study time  Mandatory class periods scheduled during the Dean s Evening Lecture Period are to be make up classes only  and cannot be in addition to the standard number of semester class periods  Also  events scheduled must not exceed the prescribed times of 7 45 p m 9 00 p m  Wednesdays and Thursdays from  7 45 p m 9 p m  2015   2016 Deans Evening Lecture Schedule   Saturday Academic Duty Schedule   Saturday Academic Duty is academic time set aside for study  8 a m 12 p m  on assigned Saturdays  Saturday mornings are shared with Military and ROTC  2015   2016 Saturday Academic Schedule   VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 